<section class="grid gap-10 py-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center lg:py-16">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <div class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-200 uppercase">
      Reflect in 3 minutes
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-300 uppercase">毎日3分、振り返って積む</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-3xl text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">
        話すだけで、
        <span class="text-slate-300">思考の地層</span>
        が静かに育つ。
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-slate-300 sm:text-lg">
        Furitsumu は、寝る前に 3 分だけ今日を話すための音声ジャーナルです。
        書くハードルをなくし、あとから読み返せる形に整えて蓄積します。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <%= link_to "無料ではじめる", new_user_registration_path, class: "rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-slate-100" %>
      <%= link_to "ログイン", new_user_session_path, class: "rounded-full border border-white/20 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-white/40" %>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400 uppercase">Short</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-white">3分で終わる</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400 uppercase">Structured</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-white">後で読める形に整理</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400 uppercase">Accumulated</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-white">続けるほど価値が増す</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/8 p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-950/40 backdrop-blur">
    <div class="rounded-[1.6rem] bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Tonight's reflection</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">05.01 Fri</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-full border border-slate-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slate-300">03:00</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 px-5 py-10 text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-24 w-24 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-slate-950 shadow-lg shadow-white/15">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.24em] uppercase">Rec</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg font-medium text-white">今日の自分に、静かに戻る。</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-400">
          録音が終わると、自動で文字起こしと
          1 行サマリーが生成されます。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
